4 Department of Finance or his/her designee;
5 (B) $5,000.00 to support the operations of the Marianas Business Network
6 to provide services that support and promote small businesses and economic
7 opportunities in the CNMI and are made equally available to the entire community,
8 expenditure authority under 2(B) shall be the Secretary of the Department of
9 Finance or his/her designee;
10 (C) $40,000.00 for the operations of the Saipan Humane Society,
11 expenditure authority under 2(C) shall be the Secretary of the Department of
